        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Beef Stroganoff. A British home-cook's dish — the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Serves 2."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A weeknight-friendly recipe: most of the work is the prep, and the cooking takes care of itself."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
